<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (bnyjy wntwạḍʿ qdạmk .. nʿln twbẗ ḥqyqyẗ
 nsjd lyk wbnṭlb wjhk .. sạybyn ṭrqnạ ạlrdyẗ)2
 ạlqrạr- tʿạl wsṭynạ .. wạsmʿ yạ rb lynạ
 ạbrỷ ạ̉rạḍynạ .. syj ḥwạlynạ
 tẖbt ḥqk fynạ .. ḥqk fynạ
 2-(bnyjy wntṣạlḥ wyạk .. wʿhwdnạ bnjddhạ mʿạk
 dy mhmạ kạnt kẖṭạyạnạ .. ạ̹ymạnạ fy gẖfrạn dmạk)2
 3-(jạyyn bnrfʿ lạsmk ạydynạ .. yạlly ạsmk duʿy ʿlynạ
 msẖtạqyn lḥḍwrk fynạ .. rwḥk yʿwd ymlk ʿlynạ)2</lyrics>
